title: Welcome To My Blog
text:
This is my first post in this Quarto blog. Welcome!

The purpose of this blog is to share hiking trips, gear, trails, orienteering games ect./br At first, primarily in Sweden but in the future anything is posible./br At the moment we are preparing for the long hike of Kungsleden (King’s Trail) in north sweden.
